    "A thick line is drawn on the border between occupational clusters and AI categories more than usual.",
    "In the figure, we sort the occupations by Ward's hierarchical clustering method, thereby creating distinct clusters.",
    "IT-related occupations (e.g., data scientists), researchers, and business-related groups (e.g., marketers) express a broad interest in generative AI, although their interest levels vary.",
    "Conversely, occupations associated with visual content (e.g., designer and photographer) display a heightened interest in imagegenerative AI tools.",
    "For the remaining occupations, there is largely an increase in interest in various generative AI tools."
